high_descs: turn around and walk over to the kitchen table at the end of the room on the right
grab an apple off of the kitchen table there
turn right and walk to the end of the room, then another right and walk over to the microwave at the end of the room
place the apple inside of the microwave, cook it, and then take it back out
turn around and walk over to the sink on your right just up ahead
place the apple inside of the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn around and go forward, then turn right to face the white table
Pick up the apple from the white table.
Turn right and go forward to the stove, then turn right to approach the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple inside and heat it up, then take the apple out.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table on the right.
Pick up the red apple on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink, then turn right and walk to the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the apple in the sink to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple in a sink.
